13 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 59 O.S. 2021, Section 396, as
14 amended by Section 1, Chapter 32, O.S.L. 2023 (59 O.S. Supp. 2024,
15 Section 396), is amended to read as follows:
16 Section 396. There is hereby re-created, to continue until July
17 1, 2024 2026, in accordance with the provisions of the Oklahoma
18 Sunset Law, the Oklahoma Funeral Board. Any reference in the
19 statutes to the Oklahoma State Board of Embalmers and Funeral
20 Directors shall be a reference to the Oklahoma Funeral Board. The
21 Board shall consist of seven (7) persons, who shall be appointed by
22 the Governor. The term of membership of each member of the Board
23 shall be five (5) years from the expiration of the term of the
24 member succeeded. Any member having served as a member of the Board
